snippet.title: N.GEN Racing (PS1) Gameplay: X-Fighter Championship
snippet.description:
X-Fighter Championship for "Contor Trophy".
My Jet is the "ADF-22 Rapier NAR-III" and it's got some serious modifications like afterburner doubler. Usually these X-Fighter races are very hard but this modification really helps. It's very expensive though, 400.000.000 Cr.
